2025-08-28GACSpecial Economic Measures ActRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Russia) Regulations Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Russia) Regulations in order to (1) lower the price cap per barrel for Russian crude oil from US$60 to US$47.60.; and (2) and makes non-substantive changes to make corrections to the names and dates of birth of individuals and the names of vessels previously listed, and to address a double listing.Registration: SOR/2025-168 Publication Date: 2025-09-10
subject: Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Russia) Regulations
precis: Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Russia) Regulations in order to (1) lower the price cap per barrel for Russian crude oil from US$60 to US$47.60.; and (2) and makes non-substantive changes to make corrections to the names and dates of birth of individuals and the names of vessels previously listed, and to address a double listing.
